<sect1 id="dir_e9d9767dc5aa2ecbd422c595afa60315_1autotoc_md590">
<title>helios::engine::modules::ui::layout</title><para>Layout primitives for UI positioning and value formatting.</para>
<para>This namespace provides fundamental layout types used by the UI system to position elements relative to their parent viewport or container, as well as components for formatting time and numeric values.</para>
</sect1>
